<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/meeting/new.css">

    <title>Nueva cita</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="box">
        <div>
            Nueva cita:
        </div>
        <form method="post" action="">
            <div id="step1">
                <div class="textBlack">
                    <input type="date" name="date" id="date">
                    <label for="date">Fecha</label>
                </div>
                <div class="textBlack">
                    <input type="time" name="hour" id="hour" required>
                    <label for="hour">Hora</label>
                </div>
                <div class="textBlack">
                    <select name="duration" id="duration" required>
                        <option value="" selected>-</option>
                        <option value="01:00">01:00</option>
                        <option value="01:30">01:30</option>
                        <option value="02:00">02:00</option>
                        <option value="02:30">02:30</option>
                        <option value="03:00">03:00</option>
                    </select>
                    <label for="duration">Duracion preferida</label>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="step2">
                <div class="textBlack">
                    <textarea name="reason" id="reason" rows="6" required></textarea>
                    <label for="reason">Motivo de la cita</label>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="step3">
                <b>Recomendaciones para tu cita:</b>
                <ul>
                    <li>Asistir con 8hr de ayuno</li>
                    <li>Ropa comoda (Ropa deportiva, tenis, etc)</li>
                    <li>Acudir abrigados en caso de frio</li>
                    <li>Usar un short extra adicional</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="control">
                <a class="btnAlert" href="/">Volver</a>
                <div>
                    <button class="btnSecondary"><i class="fi fi-sr-arrow-left"></i></button>
                    <button class="btnSecondary"><i class="fi fi-sr-arrow-right"></i></button>
                    <a href="" class="btnPrimary"><i class="fi fi-sr-check"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>